public class AeRecoveredItemsSet
extends java.util.LinkedHashMap
implements IAeRecoveredItemsSet

Implements a set of recovered items representing alarm and queue manager requests. Extends LinkedHashMap to preserve order of insertion for getRecoveredItems().
